Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“年轻人 为何徘徊于此”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我在寻找着阳光 却迷失了方向”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多用丹田发声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让声音能穿越这油泥海到达对岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能传得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是开开心心搞文化节的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词都已经倒背如流了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来问题出在这手上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得交臂的时候 你总被我先抓住领子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“追寻阳光却为何来到这不见天日的森林?”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好迟呀 明之 而且那是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚要出门 我老妈就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许找借口 你的角色一直都是古市在顶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手张开给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只手也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“然后这名老翁便抓住年轻人的双手”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“试起了他的腕力”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“然而影子却是因阳光而生的”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把别人压在自己的阴影下 感觉很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市 你…被希洛克…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校车爆炸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实在那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被选中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止我是怀着什么样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 该由我来给你安排角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之 你想法使女人远离那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个扎穆德已经迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个希洛克因为憎恨而进化了 没救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退远点好好看着吧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁是光 谁是影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的眼睛确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是只用憎恨喂食希洛克的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 你会被希洛克的怨恨所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去的话就说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…想…活…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 已经连扎穆德的面貌都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得刚才有点火大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛非得祈求那家伙不可?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫不懂人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我心情舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是你的敌人吧 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说你的敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生气了 古市 快给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 当影子要更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漆黑的夜里 谁都找不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么呼喊 都不会有人来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是从什么时候开始的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始觉得阳光太耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 是自从遇到了你以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这都已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 我会成为光 这家伙才是影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 有件事你要明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢明之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 连你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜次上这样一个无聊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生一个随处可见的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阴郁又无聊的日子里 找到点微不足道的幸福就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所期望的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说你是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就没真正喜欢过一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你知不知道这很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然被这种小狐狸精迷住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不谨慎了 小明之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 真是的 怎么能随便跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚醒来的春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么处置那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 谁让他这么耀眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光也好影也好 古市就是古市 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成不了光的话 还怎么照耀你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我也能成为像你一样的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 说“是”吧 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在那时候被选中的人 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安静点行不行 快点去死行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 那个女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要藏好了 春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩远走高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都搞错了 这世界太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 就无法救回那个女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能杀了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寻找着阳光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却迷失了…方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你自己也会回不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于庞大的憎恨阻碍了石化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你真是个傻瓜 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会恢复原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以找龙藏医生商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会像以前一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人就像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候怎么就不下场雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晴朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空 蓝得过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认命中 对象停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 发射实弹须经许可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASP是用来守护这个岛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知这样 我才不会当什么主魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我认为这也是在守护这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 不会杀他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不少事情需要这两位帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说“这两只”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,己方人员中居然会有扎穆德诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是犯人 不会对她动粗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉打扰你的重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有不少事情要问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢藏小秘密的西村春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿到我的房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 请带上面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 怪闷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 您是说这怪物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有一个女人 把她找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该…怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 娜琪亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才把你丢出去 很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还得回故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没赶来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要犹豫 让他们立即开船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会追上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是赶不上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在赞巴尼号上等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 在后面 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急着开火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确保中佐的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我把中佐放开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动 快松手 你这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我疏忽大意 咎由自取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么… 中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要给扎穆德致命的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这些没经历过战争的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特务编队紧急呼叫第7区及其周边各人员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,01号监视目标 竹原明之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挟持垣巢中佐后逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 带着中佐逃跑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽大意 万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的收容准备刚完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 市区周边已部署了重装警队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围ASP也正在展开中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将西村春和寺冈古市分开送往这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可能会有与扎穆德接触的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待中佐的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对扎穆德究竟会说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候越是无知的人越容易抓住真相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我有点困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该如何跟你交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白我的话吗 竹原明之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我的性命总是辗转于你们父子手中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我老爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲是我的战友 同时也是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能冷静的跟你谈几句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把手松开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会加害春和古市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人对我而言都是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能给你们安排一个生存的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个泰斯克的少女曾跟你在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能告诉我更多关于你们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪力 骨折了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发现垣巢中佐 己经发现垣巢中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹原明之目前依然在逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护送车3号 1号 报告现在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护送车1号 现在正通过商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号骨骼呼叫1号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现对象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 三分钟左右会合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达前不要开火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来 停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号骨骼呼叫2号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在位置是北面8加普
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 你在干什么 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 好迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你好受的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐真生气的时候 可是很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载着古市的护送车失去联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可能去的地方 或者值得留恋的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢 阿婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿好像抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我三瓶冰镇的弹珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等会儿 我去给你把冰得最透的拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人喝得了那么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心得蛀牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瓶是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瓶是给最爱的春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一瓶就给我最…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抵抗的话 就不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 大家直到最后都要多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面容也好 生命也好…都是因为会消逝才显得美丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连可以入土为安的故乡都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我真不明白你们的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还未成年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这时候那些家伙也在什么地方仰望这轮明月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪越大就越不想动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你能从坟墓里爬起来 往我后面踹上一脚?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起来 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么 连话都不会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁捡来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字…是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个难叫醒的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个漂泊在北国的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人偶然相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡不醒的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行于雪国的愁苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价实在太高了

